  "_note": "calendar depth lane — the full-fidelity calendar view over five shapes: `events` (a date field + a colored select → all-day colored events, the full view set + week numbers, drag-select create, click-to-edit, delete; ev_7 is deliberately undated and must stay off the grid), `stays` (from/to span → multi-day events, resizable), `meetings` (a dateTime field + a recurrence text field → timed events, timeGrid week/day, business hours + now indicator + slots, a weekly recurring row), `timed` (start/finish dateTime span → the time-grid PRECISION surface: an overlapping pair on 2026-08-03 for side-by-side layout, events across the workday, an all-day + a 23:00 late event to prove 24h reachability, resizable-from-either-edge), `plain` (no date field → the graceful misconfigured chip). Dates sit in 2026-08; journeys anchor the view there via the persisted calDate + calView. Booted by journeys/extra/calendar-view.mjs on the lane band (5891).",
